headline: LENNAR ANNOUNCES STILLWATER COMMUNITY COMING TO LAKEWOOD RANCH
summary: Lennar, one of the nation's leading homebuilders, announces Stillwater, a new gated residential community coming soon to Lakewood Ranch, Florida, the top-selling multi-generational master-planned community in the U.S., according to RCLCO, a real estate advisory firm. Nestled among natural preserves, Stillwater offers a peaceful, private setting with easy access to nearby urban conveniences. headline: United Rentals' Q2 Earnings Miss Estimates, Revenues Up Y/Y
summary: URI's second-quarter results reflect strong demand in core rental operations. The company sees soft used equipment sales.
